Mobile Internet. They want to save their valuable mobile data by installing lot of mobile data wrecking browser extension in Mozilla until they got some intriguing results. In order to do so an amazing tool has grabbed the attention of thousands of Bangladeshi surfers. Inspectlet has debuting all over Bangladeshi social media and has already marked its presence.

Getting Started With Inspectlet

It is so easy to use Inspectlet. All you have to do is to choose one from the most popular browsers, install Inspectlet Extension from Mozilla, Firefox, Chrome to Opera. The extension looks like bes virus. After installing it just have to login to Inspectlet services using the email address you used with the browser. The tracking of the activities performed by the user will do by the Inspectlet extension. The extension is available for individual and business purpose and so, the services vary.

Personal

Personal account allow the users to give permission to 10 systems only which are also called Dashboards. The users can also see live video recording of their website visitors or guests. The data can be exported about 10 times after login or the customers can get help from customer service. More than ten users can get the account by Business plan. So, a personal account user must get in good relationship with the customer service.

Business

Business account let the users access up to their 100 dashboards. The users can also store numerous data and export more than 30 times after logging
